rgence of the magnetic field, and is\nnot present in previous models due to insufficient resolution. This hardening\ncould be observed with a coordinated flare observation from active radio\nobservatories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Mar 2019 11:15:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-12"}
